Package net.tnemc.core.compatibility

Interface ServerConnector

All Known Implementing Classes:
BukkitServerProvider, FabricServerProvider, FoliaServerProvider, PaperServerProvider, SpongeServerProvider
public interface ServerConnector
Acts like a bridge between various server software and classes specific to each server software such as opening menus, and sending messages.
Since:
0.1.2.0
Author:
creatorfromhell
